# Be Civic project marker (detection-only).
#
# The be-civic plugin's gate skill checks for this file (or one in a parent
# directory) to detect that the conversation is running inside a Be Civic
# project, and the preamble uses it to resolve the project folder. When present,
# the project's CLAUDE.md harness is treated as the active session context and
# the gate skill exits quietly.
#
# Everything Be Civic lives inside this one project folder: user-visible state
# (CLAUDE.md, MEMORY.md, profile data, documents/, research notes) at the root,
# and agent-managed state (the harness key, registries, session buffers) under
# the hidden .be-civic/state/ subdirectory beside this file. There is no
# separate location to point at — this marker carries detection metadata only.
#
# Fields below are filled in at setup. Do not put any private information here.
#
#   user_id        the pseudonymous identity id
#   plugin_version the be-civic plugin version that created the project
#   created_at     ISO-8601 UTC timestamp of project creation
#
user_id=<user_id>
plugin_version=<plugin_version>
created_at=<RFC3339 UTC timestamp>
#
# Do not delete this file unless you want to convert the folder back to a
# non-Be-Civic folder.
